84
00:04:19.592 --> 00:04:20.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well...</c.bg_transparent>

85
00:04:21.010 --> 00:04:23.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
