90
00:04:35.817 --> 00:04:37.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>this charming fellow either.</c.bg_transparent>

91
00:04:37.402 --> 00:04:40.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, how perfectly brilliant of you.</c.bg_transparent>

92
00:04:42.073 --> 00:04:45.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor, I want to know everything</c.bg_transparent>
