<c.bg_transparent>How much do you know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about carbon reaction chambers?</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:07:20.690 --> 00:07:22.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've learned</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a little about laser-induced fusion</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:07:23.025 --> 00:07:24.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>not much more than the basics.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:07:24.444 --> 00:07:26.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, it's a bloody inefficient system.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:07:26.612 --> 00:07:29.073 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd trade it in for a Federation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>model tomorrow if I could</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:07:29.157 --> 00:07:30.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>but it's all we've got.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:07:30.741 --> 00:07:31.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do me a favor.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:07:31.909 --> 00:07:34.036 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep an eye on the exhaust</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>plasma temperature.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:07:36.581 --> 00:07:41.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, increase deuterium flow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by five percent to reaction chamber two.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:07:41.752 --> 00:07:43.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Procedure is not recommended.</i></c.bg_transparent>

113
00:07:43.754 --> 00:07:46.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, I've had enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your opinions, damn it.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:07:46.257 --> 00:07:47.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just do it!</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:07:47.341 --> 00:07:48.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Procedure is not recommended.</i></c.bg_transparent>

116
00:07:49.051 --> 00:07:54.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Consult Cardassian operational guidelines</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>paragraph 254-A, now on screen.</i></c.bg_transparent>

117
00:07:54.974 --> 00:07:59.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to read your tech manual.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Fine. We'll do it ourselves.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:08:02.148 --> 00:08:03.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reinitializing reactor two.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:08:05.151 --> 00:08:10.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Directing plasma flow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to conduits 143, 144...</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:08:10.198 --> 00:08:12.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief O'Brien, the power</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>flow from reactor two</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:08:12.325 --> 00:08:13.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>has just been shut down.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:08:13.409 --> 00:08:14.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:08:14.994 --> 00:08:17.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, analyze reactor two failure.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:20.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Reactor two was shut down</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>after sensors detected</i></c.bg_transparent>

125
00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:23.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>a potential overload</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>of the carbon reaction chambers.</i></c.bg_transparent>

126
00:08:24.837 --> 00:08:26.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it. That's the straw!</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:08:26.589 --> 00:08:28.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Relax, Chief. It's just a computer.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:08:29.091 --> 00:08:32.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is no computer. This is my archenemy.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:08:32.386 --> 00:08:34.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've got it working just fine,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as far I can tell.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:08:34.388 --> 00:08:37.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fine? With all due respect, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:37.141 --> 00:08:39.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As an engineer,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I couldn't look at myself in the mirror</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:08:39.143 --> 00:08:42.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>if I allowed this computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to continue to perform as it is now.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:08:42.939 --> 00:08:44.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to do a root canal.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:08:44.565 --> 00:08:45.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Root canal?</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:08:45.566 --> 00:08:48.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's engineering shorthand, sir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to get into its guts.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:08:48.903 --> 00:08:51.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-and rebuild it from the ground up.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-How long will that take?</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:08:51.948 --> 00:08:54.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm still not that familiar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with Cardassian technology</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:08:54.408 --> 00:08:57.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but, oh, I guess no more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than two, three years.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:08:57.870 --> 00:09:01.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's going to take a lot of man-hours.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Is it really necessary?</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:01.415 --> 00:09:02.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't understand--</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:09:02.833 --> 00:09:05.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's just say I don't have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your sensitivity to the computer.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:09:06.796 --> 00:09:08.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's all right. Forget about it.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:09:08.589 --> 00:09:10.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Uh, Chief...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's all right. It doesn't matter.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:09:10.508 --> 00:09:13.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief, I want you to do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you have to do.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:09:14.428 --> 00:09:16.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, sir. I'll get right on it.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:09:18.015 --> 00:09:22.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And this is Ops.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The heart and soul of Deep Space 9.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:09:22.770 --> 00:09:24.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, there you are, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:09:25.189 --> 00:09:27.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gentlemen, Madam Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:09:27.692 --> 00:09:30.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They insisted on seeing operations, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:09:30.403 --> 00:09:31.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:09:32.029 --> 00:09:35.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Make yourselves at home.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I trust that Doctor Bashir</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:09:35.491 --> 00:09:37.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>has been taking care of all your needs.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:09:37.868 --> 00:09:41.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, he refuses to change</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my accommodations.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:09:41.455 --> 00:09:42.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Accommodations?</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:09:42.707 --> 00:09:45.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, if I have to sleep another night</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:09:45.459 --> 00:09:48.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>on a Cardassian bed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with gargoyles staring at me</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:09:48.754 --> 00:09:50.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>from the wood poles...</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:09:50.256 --> 00:09:51.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:09:51.799 --> 00:09:54.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>An unidentified vessel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is coming through the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:09:54.594 --> 00:09:56.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On screen. Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:09:57.638 --> 00:09:59.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, you'll get a better view</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from over here.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:10:08.691 --> 00:10:10.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quite a sight isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:10:11.569 --> 00:10:14.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it? That's the whole thing?</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:10:14.864 --> 00:10:15.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, yes, it is.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:10:16.365 --> 00:10:17.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was expecting more, somehow.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:10:18.492 --> 00:10:21.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: Scanners aren't picking up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any life-forms on board.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:10:21.662 --> 00:10:23.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-A probe?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Might be.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:10:24.415 --> 00:10:26.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm reading an extensive computer array</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:10:26.626 --> 00:10:29.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but no signals to suggest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's trying to maintain contact</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:10:29.128 --> 00:10:30.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with a mother ship.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:10:30.463 --> 00:10:32.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are the computers compatible with ours?</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:10:33.007 --> 00:10:34.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's hard to tell.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:10:34.383 --> 00:10:37.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't recognize any known</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>subprocessor patterns.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:10:37.637 --> 00:10:40.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Obviously, the young woman</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doesn't have the necessary experience.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:10:40.181 --> 00:10:41.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps I can--</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:10:41.223 --> 00:10:45.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The "young woman" over there</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has over 300 years experience, Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:10:45.770 --> 00:10:48.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: I might have better luck</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if we towed it into the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:10:49.357 --> 00:10:51.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, not until we know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a little bit more about it.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:10:52.401 --> 00:10:54.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, tow it to 500 meters</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>off the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:10:54.987 --> 00:10:55.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:10:56.072 --> 00:10:58.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. O'Brien, try to set up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>an adaptive interface link</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:10:58.491 --> 00:11:00.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and see if we can download</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any information from it.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:11:00.910 --> 00:11:01.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:11:04.330 --> 00:11:07.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it will be best</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if we clear this area.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:11:07.958 --> 00:11:10.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But this probe may represent contact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with a new species.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:11:11.128 --> 00:11:12.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander, I think it would be appropriate</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:11:12.880 --> 00:11:16.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for at least one Federation ambassador</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be present at this historic occasion</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:11:16.509 --> 00:11:20.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and since I have a particular interest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in First Contact procedures...</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:11:20.221 --> 00:11:22.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I appreciate your interest, Ambassador</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:11:22.306 --> 00:11:25.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and to keep you all informed,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm scheduling a briefing</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:11:25.351 --> 00:11:29.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>at 0400. In the meantime, Dr. Bashir</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the best place to view this probe</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:11:30.189 --> 00:11:32.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is from the docking ring near Port Seven.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:11:33.025 --> 00:11:34.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll show them the way.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:11:45.287 --> 00:11:46.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:11:59.093 --> 00:12:00.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Such concentration.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:12:01.720 --> 00:12:04.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Such intensity, such passion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for your work.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:12:05.433 --> 00:12:07.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tracking intergalactic malefactors.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:12:09.520 --> 00:12:11.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Most people find it rather tedious.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:12:12.064 --> 00:12:14.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tedious? ( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:12:14.442 --> 00:12:18.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, those of us who have been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>beneficiaries of your heroism</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:12:18.612 --> 00:12:20.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>would never call your work tedious.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:12:21.282 --> 00:12:22.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've learned that, on this station</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:12:23.242 --> 00:12:27.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you are the thin, beige line</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>between order and chaos.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:12:28.622 --> 00:12:29.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's my job.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:12:30.916 --> 00:12:35.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, what can I do for you?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You haven't lost anything else, I hope.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:12:36.589 --> 00:12:37.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Only my heart.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:12:38.841 --> 00:12:39.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I beg your pardon?</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:12:41.177 --> 00:12:42.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is, um...</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:12:43.053 --> 00:12:45.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is Odo your first or last name?</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:12:46.682 --> 00:12:47.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:12:47.766 --> 00:12:50.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh. Then I can just call you, uh?</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:12:50.978 --> 00:12:51.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:12:53.272 --> 00:12:55.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It has a certain lyrical quality.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:12:56.984 --> 00:12:57.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lyrical?</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:12:58.360 --> 00:12:59.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo...</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:12:59.987 --> 00:13:01.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It rolls off the tongue.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:13:03.157 --> 00:13:03.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh...</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:13:04.742 --> 00:13:07.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have a lot of work to do.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:13:07.912 --> 00:13:09.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand you're a shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:13:10.623 --> 00:13:11.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's correct.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:13:11.624 --> 00:13:13.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never been with a shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:13:15.461 --> 00:13:16.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Been with?"</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:13:17.338 --> 00:13:19.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've heard</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you're the only one of your kind.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:13:21.717 --> 00:13:22.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So far.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:13:23.969 --> 00:13:26.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mmm. All the men I've known</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:13:26.722 --> 00:13:30.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>have needed to be shaped,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and molded, and manipulated</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:13:30.267 --> 00:13:31.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and finally I've met a man</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:13:32.311 --> 00:13:34.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>who knows how to do it himself.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:13:35.898 --> 00:13:36.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:13:38.442 --> 00:13:41.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning ) Is that the com?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I think it is. Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:13:41.529 --> 00:13:42.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got to get to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:14:00.214 --> 00:14:05.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Initiating high-resolution scan.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Memory nodes located.</i></c.bg_transparent>

233
00:14:05.511 --> 00:14:07.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Proceeding with data transfer.</i></c.bg_transparent>

234
00:14:08.013 --> 00:14:10.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, there you go.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Who would have thought?</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:14:11.016 --> 00:14:12.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You seem surprised, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:14:12.685 --> 00:14:14.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, knowing this computer,</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:14:14.186 --> 00:14:16.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought I would have had to reconfigure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the whole emulator module</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:14:16.605 --> 00:14:20.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to make it compatible with the probe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but it's cooperating for once.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:14:22.152 --> 00:14:24.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Transfer of data is complete.</i></c.bg_transparent>

240
00:14:25.072 --> 00:14:26.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well done, computer.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:14:27.616 --> 00:14:31.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, run standard code translations</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on probe data.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:14:31.203 --> 00:14:32.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Isolate syntax results.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:14:33.289 --> 00:14:34.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Processing.</i></c.bg_transparent>

244
00:14:34.623 --> 00:14:35.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

245
00:14:40.045 --> 00:14:41.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come in. Yes, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:14:42.172 --> 00:14:43.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander...</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:14:44.258 --> 00:14:46.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I have a problem.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Quark again?</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:14:46.302 --> 00:14:49.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, sir. This one is named Lwaxana.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:14:49.597 --> 00:14:51.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lwaxana Troi, the ambassador?</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:14:51.682 --> 00:14:52.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's her.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:14:53.142 --> 00:14:57.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was a minor incident at the bar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that I helped her with, and now she's...</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:14:58.939 --> 00:14:59.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Grateful.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:15:00.691 --> 00:15:01.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's the problem?</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:15:02.359 --> 00:15:05.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The manner in which</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she expresses her... gratitude.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:15:06.572 --> 00:15:08.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To be honest, Commander, she seems...</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:15:09.867 --> 00:15:11.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Interested in me.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:15:13.662 --> 00:15:14.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong with that?</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:15:16.790 --> 00:15:18.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's extremely aggressive.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:15:18.667 --> 00:15:21.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see. So she's after you.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:15:22.087 --> 00:15:24.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Like a Wanoni tracehound.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:15:24.715 --> 00:15:26.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you thought of letting her catch you?</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:15:27.635 --> 00:15:28.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir?</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:15:29.136 --> 00:15:30.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A little romance, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:15:31.430 --> 00:15:35.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have six pylons that need a complete</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>security sweep.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:15:35.225 --> 00:15:38.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't have time for romantic interludes.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:15:42.316 --> 00:15:45.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Frankly, in my humble opinion,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>most of you humanoids</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:15:45.110 --> 00:15:49.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>spend far too much time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on your respective mating rituals.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:15:49.823 --> 00:15:52.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It does help the procreation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of one's species.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:15:52.952 --> 00:15:56.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Procreation does not require</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>changing how you smell</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:15:56.580 --> 00:16:00.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>or writing bad poetry,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or sacrificing various plants</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:16:00.751 --> 00:16:03.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to serve as tokens of affection.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:16:04.755 --> 00:16:07.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In any event,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's all irrelevant to me.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:16:07.925 --> 00:16:09.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry to hear that.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:16:10.010 --> 00:16:13.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would appreciate it if you would do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>something about this woman.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:16:13.472 --> 00:16:14.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me?</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:16:14.598 --> 00:16:17.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just tell her to leave me alone.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:16:17.559 --> 00:16:21.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Constable, you can handle thieves</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and killers, but not one Betazoid woman?</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:16:21.772 --> 00:16:26.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand thieves and killers.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand... her.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:16:27.319 --> 00:16:28.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't help you, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:16:29.071 --> 00:16:32.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm just trying to avoid</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a diplomatic incident.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:16:32.157 --> 00:16:33.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to insult the Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:16:34.201 --> 00:16:35.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: A reasonable concern.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:16:35.953 --> 00:16:39.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suggest you handle the matter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with great delicacy.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:16:44.420 --> 00:16:48.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't handle "delicacy" very well.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:16:52.261 --> 00:16:55.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The probe appears to be made out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of some sort of corundium alloy.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:16:56.598 --> 00:16:59.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Analysis of all subprocessor</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>modules is complete.</i></c.bg_transparent>

287
00:17:00.728 --> 00:17:01.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Already?</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:17:02.730 --> 00:17:03.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On screen.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:17:05.566 --> 00:17:06.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant?</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:17:11.321 --> 00:17:14.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No science modules</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no communications system</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:17:14.700 --> 00:17:18.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and enough computer capacity to run</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a Galaxy-class starship.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:17:18.370 --> 00:17:19.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's very odd.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:17:20.164 --> 00:17:23.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's an awful lot of computer hardware</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>simply to navigate a probe.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:17:23.250 --> 00:17:24.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anything?</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:17:25.127 --> 00:17:27.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing to suggest the probe's mission...</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:17:27.629 --> 00:17:29.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or any hint of its origin.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:17:37.806 --> 00:17:39.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah! There you are, Odo!</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:17:40.059 --> 00:17:44.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs ) Have you ever been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the fourth moon of Andevian II at dawn?</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:17:44.438 --> 00:17:45.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can't say I have.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:17:46.065 --> 00:17:49.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have the most wonderful holoprogram.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And I've reserved a suite for us</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:17:49.568 --> 00:17:50.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with that Quark person.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:17:51.320 --> 00:17:54.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You told Quark that you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were going into a holosuite with me?</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:17:54.114 --> 00:17:54.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, of course.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:17:55.032 --> 00:17:57.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's preparing a special</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>picnic basket for us.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:17:57.201 --> 00:17:58.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good Lord.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:17:58.660 --> 00:17:59.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm afraid I'm not available.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:18:00.079 --> 00:18:02.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to get</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to Upper Pylon 3 immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:18:02.498 --> 00:18:03.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Ambassador...</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:18:03.499 --> 00:18:04.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, Lwaxana.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:18:05.209 --> 00:18:07.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um... Upper Pylon 3.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:18:07.711 --> 00:18:10.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've always wanted to see an upper pylon.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:18:13.008 --> 00:18:16.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, I'll have Quark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>send one of his minions with our basket.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:18:17.054 --> 00:18:18.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll have our picnic up there.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:18:18.472 --> 00:18:19.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Ambassador...</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:18:19.640 --> 00:18:21.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, Lwaxana.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:18:21.558 --> 00:18:25.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't eat. This is not a real mouth.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:18:25.604 --> 00:18:30.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is an approximation of one.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I do not have an esophagus or a stomach</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:18:30.400 --> 00:18:33.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or a digestive system. I am not like you.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:18:33.737 --> 00:18:38.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every 16 hours, I turn into a liquid.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:18:39.284 --> 00:18:40.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can swim.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:18:40.452 --> 00:18:41.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh!</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:18:45.624 --> 00:18:46.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer?</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:18:47.876 --> 00:18:48.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer!</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:18:51.547 --> 00:18:52.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:18:53.006 --> 00:18:54.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:18:54.925 --> 00:18:57.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
