329
00:19:06.103 --> 00:19:09.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're reading a turbolift failure, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We'll beam you out.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:19:09.940 --> 00:19:12.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Locking on. Prepare to transport.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:19:12.317 --> 00:19:13.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Ready.</i></c.bg_transparent>

332
00:19:13.527 --> 00:19:14.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Energizing.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:19:21.118 --> 00:19:21.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well?</c.bg_transparent>

334
