335
00:19:24.454 --> 00:19:25.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>But don't worry, Constable.</i></c.bg_transparent>

336
00:19:25.873 --> 00:19:27.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We'll get it repaired right away.</i></c.bg_transparent>

337
00:19:28.458 --> 00:19:31.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax to Chief O'Brien.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Please report to Ops immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:19:32.337 --> 00:19:33.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be patient, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:19:33.255 --> 00:19:35.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We'll get you out of there</i></c.bg_transparent>
