342
00:19:59.198 --> 00:20:01.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Load detection functions, normal.</i></c.bg_transparent>

343
00:20:02.034 --> 00:20:03.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Diagnostic complete.</i></c.bg_transparent>

344
00:20:03.952 --> 00:20:05.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't get it.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:20:05.787 --> 00:20:09.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every component of the turbolift power net</c.bg_transparent>
