351
00:20:22.679 --> 00:20:23.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>there's no telling how long it'll take.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:20:24.014 --> 00:20:24.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get it started.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:20:27.768 --> 00:20:28.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kira to Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:20:28.852 --> 00:20:29.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Yes, Major?</i></c.bg_transparent>

355
00:20:30.020 --> 00:20:32.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, but you're going</c.bg_transparent>
