<c.bg_transparent>Define "a while."</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:20:35.025 --> 00:20:36.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I knew.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:20:38.320 --> 00:20:40.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>By the way, Cardassian turbolifts</i></c.bg_transparent>

359
00:20:40.948 --> 00:20:42.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
