361
00:20:44.451 --> 00:20:46.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>so don't try to shape-shift your way out.</i></c.bg_transparent>

362
00:20:48.080 --> 00:20:49.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wouldn't think of it.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:20:51.541 --> 00:20:53.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Besides, it wouldn't be polite.</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:20:53.752 --> 00:20:54.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I didn't hear that.</i></c.bg_transparent>

365
00:20:57.172 --> 00:20:58.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I--It wouldn't be polite.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:20:59.007 --> 00:21:01.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Understood. Kira out.</i></c.bg_transparent>

367
