<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:21:05.889 --> 00:21:09.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you suppose that we're, uh...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we're actually in any danger?</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:21:10.060 --> 00:21:11.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not if we remain calm.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:21:12.020 --> 00:21:12.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:21:13.981 --> 00:21:17.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, then we might as well</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>enjoy ourselves.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:21:17.693 --> 00:21:20.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, we can take the opportunity</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get to know each other.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:21:22.281 --> 00:21:25.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd really prefer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to pass the time quietly.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:21:26.660 --> 00:21:27.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Quietly.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Quietly.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:21:27.828 --> 00:21:28.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Of course.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:21:29.079 --> 00:21:29.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mmm.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:21:35.752 --> 00:21:37.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:21:37.879 --> 00:21:39.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The quiet man.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:21:39.923 --> 00:21:40.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:21:41.883 --> 00:21:44.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've always been attracted to quiet men.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:21:45.637 --> 00:21:46.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odd, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:21:47.472 --> 00:21:51.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But maybe there's more truth than</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we realize to that old axiom that op--</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:21:54.604 --> 00:21:55.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quietly.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:22:06.742 --> 00:22:07.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:22:09.494 --> 00:22:10.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes?</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:22:11.580 --> 00:22:12.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think I can.</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:22:16.084 --> 00:22:17.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can what?</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:22:18.503 --> 00:22:22.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
