389
00:22:22.257 --> 00:22:25.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I, I think I really need to talk.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:22:26.720 --> 00:22:27.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:22:30.265 --> 00:22:31.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:22:37.022 --> 00:22:38.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's nothing to be afraid of.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:22:39.149 --> 00:22:40.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course not.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:22:40.859 --> 00:22:43.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, things could be much worse.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:22:44.029 --> 00:22:44.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really?</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:22:44.946 --> 00:22:46.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:22:46.573 --> 00:22:48.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My daughter and I were once trapped</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:22:48.742 --> 00:22:51.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>aboard a Ferengi cargo ship,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and it was dreadful.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:22:51.661 --> 00:22:54.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, all right,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it wasn't actually dreadful.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:22:54.998 --> 00:22:56.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was mildly lamentable</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:22:57.292 --> 00:23:00.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and it was all because</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of that loathsome DaiMon.</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:23:00.378 --> 00:23:01.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well...</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:23:01.379 --> 00:23:04.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, he wasn't altogether loathsome.</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:23:04.216 --> 00:23:06.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was just slightly repulsive.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:23:07.511 --> 00:23:13.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But he did have a certain charm</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in an insufferable kind of way.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:23:15.018 --> 00:23:19.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course, he was totally at the mercy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of his uncontrollable passion for me</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:23:19.314 --> 00:23:22.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>which means he wasn't all bad,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>now, doesn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:23:23.193 --> 00:23:25.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you know, it wasn't all passion, no.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:23:26.029 --> 00:23:29.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was some negligible</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>commercial interest involved</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:23:29.908 --> 00:23:35.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but, oh, the passion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>oh, that was... that was perfectly real</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:23:35.413 --> 00:23:38.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and kind of, um, kind of sweet in a way.</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:23:39.292 --> 00:23:41.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was so helpless.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:23:41.503 --> 00:23:44.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At first, it was totally</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a question of expediency</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:23:44.840 --> 00:23:46.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>when I made love with--with him.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:23:47.384 --> 00:23:48.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you looking at?</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:23:49.761 --> 00:23:50.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:23:50.971 --> 00:23:51.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:23:51.888 --> 00:23:52.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:23:53.098 --> 00:23:53.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:23:54.850 --> 00:24:00.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was just wondering how many volts</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are in that exposed circuit.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:24:00.564 --> 00:24:02.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on. Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:24:02.691 --> 00:24:06.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well... frankly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by the time one thing led to another...</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:24:08.572 --> 00:24:12.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Think of it as an opportunity, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You never know when a friendly ambassador</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:24:12.159 --> 00:24:15.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>is going to be in the right place</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the right time to help your career.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:24:15.287 --> 00:24:18.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Another hour with them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could destroy my career.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:24:18.582 --> 00:24:22.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a simple job.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Just keep them happy and away from me.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:24:22.460 --> 00:24:23.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Simple?</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:24:23.753 --> 00:24:25.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing makes them happy.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:24:26.089 --> 00:24:28.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are dedicated to being unhappy</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:24:28.300 --> 00:24:30.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and to spreading that unhappiness</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wherever they go.</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:24:30.594 --> 00:24:33.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are the Ambassadors of Unhappy.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:24:33.513 --> 00:24:34.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:24:35.056 --> 00:24:36.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of us have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>had these assignments, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:24:36.892 --> 00:24:37.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you, sir?</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:24:37.893 --> 00:24:41.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As a matter of fact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon Dax used to take perverse pleasure</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:24:41.188 --> 00:24:43.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>in assigning me to take care</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of VIP guests.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:24:43.523 --> 00:24:46.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, so now you take the same</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>perverse pleasure.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:24:46.484 --> 00:24:47.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In doing it to me.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:24:48.153 --> 00:24:49.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:24:50.113 --> 00:24:51.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May I ask, sir</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:24:51.114 --> 00:24:54.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>when you graduated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from this sort of assignment?</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:24:57.078 --> 00:24:59.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The day I hit one of the guests.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:25:00.457 --> 00:25:01.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hit one...</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:25:02.459 --> 00:25:05.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was a simple misunderstanding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>over his attempt to coax a young Ensign</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:25:05.712 --> 00:25:07.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to his quarters against her will.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:25:09.883 --> 00:25:10.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But...</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:25:13.136 --> 00:25:14.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't hit one of them, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:25:14.930 --> 00:25:17.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not nearly as understanding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as Curzon was.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:25:18.016 --> 00:25:19.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:25:20.352 --> 00:25:22.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O'Brien: Commander, can I talk to you?</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:25:26.233 --> 00:25:29.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's about the computer, sir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Still giving you problems?</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:25:29.194 --> 00:25:31.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, sir, that's just the thing, it's not.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:25:31.279 --> 00:25:33.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It rerouted the EPS power flow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in less than an hour.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:25:33.865 --> 00:25:35.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's good news.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:25:35.158 --> 00:25:37.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How soon can we get Odo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the Ambassador out?</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:25:37.369 --> 00:25:40.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It didn't activate the turbolift circuits.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:25:40.413 --> 00:25:41.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't ask me why.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:25:41.915 --> 00:25:43.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must have some idea of what's wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:25:44.626 --> 00:25:45.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to listen to something.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:25:46.711 --> 00:25:51.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, analyze Ops 0-2 sensor readings.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:25:52.467 --> 00:25:58.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>All sensors read between 14.3</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and 14.4 KSC.</i></c.bg_transparent>

462
00:26:02.102 --> 00:26:06.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, restart all shield</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>generator subsystems.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:26:06.898 --> 00:26:09.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Shield generator subsystems</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>set to active status.</i></c.bg_transparent>

464
00:26:09.818 --> 00:26:12.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Reading 98.3% efficiency.</i></c.bg_transparent>

465
00:26:12.862 --> 00:26:14.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whispering ) Do you hear it?</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:26:16.783 --> 00:26:18.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whispering ) Hear what?</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:26:18.159 --> 00:26:20.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The voice, it's not the same attitude.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:26:20.745 --> 00:26:22.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It sounds like the computer.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:26:23.164 --> 00:26:25.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, when you work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with a computer as much as I do</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:26:25.417 --> 00:26:28.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you get to know it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They're all very different.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:26:28.336 --> 00:26:31.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Working with the</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Enterprise </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was like dancing a waltz.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:26:31.589 --> 00:26:34.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>With this computer, it's always</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>been like a wrestling match</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:26:34.467 --> 00:26:36.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>till we started downloading the probe.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:26:36.678 --> 00:26:38.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You think some kind of program</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the probe</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:26:38.722 --> 00:26:40.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is influencing our computer?</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:26:40.557 --> 00:26:42.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, it's got to be more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than just a program, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:26:43.059 --> 00:26:45.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The computer's whole personality</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has changed.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:26:46.146 --> 00:26:48.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not resisting any commands</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:26:48.398 --> 00:26:51.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>offering any opinions,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>giving any arguments</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:26:52.319 --> 00:26:56.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and there's this one other crazy thing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm almost afraid to mention.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:26:56.156 --> 00:26:57.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:26:57.699 --> 00:27:01.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every time I leave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>something happens to bring me back.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:27:01.161 --> 00:27:02.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bring you back?</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:27:02.579 --> 00:27:07.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To the computer like the failures</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the turbolifts and the transporters.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:27:07.334 --> 00:27:09.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A few minutes ago, I was working</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the transporter pad</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:27:09.502 --> 00:27:13.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the com lines went down</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and when I broke for a quick bite to eat</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:27:13.882 --> 00:27:15.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we had a replicator failure.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:27:15.884 --> 00:27:19.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's almost like the computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doesn't want me to leave it alone.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:27:20.013 --> 00:27:22.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You almost make it sound like a child.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:27:32.150 --> 00:27:34.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Station Log, supplemental.</i></c.bg_transparent>

491
00:27:34.235 --> 00:27:37.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Odo and Ambassador Troi</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>remain trapped in Turbolift 4.</i></c.bg_transparent>

492
00:27:37.822 --> 00:27:40.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>As of yet, we have been unable</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to ascertain what it is</i></c.bg_transparent>

493
00:27:40.825 --> 00:27:43.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>that's causing the station's computer</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to malfunction.</i></c.bg_transparent>

494
00:27:44.412 --> 00:27:47.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if it's some kind</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of non biological life-form</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:27:47.332 --> 00:27:48.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we've never seen before?</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:27:48.625 --> 00:27:49.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nonbiological?</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:27:50.418 --> 00:27:53.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, it all comes down</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to how we define life-form.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:27:53.546 --> 00:27:57.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But just as biological organisms</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have evolved in our cultures</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:27:57.300 --> 00:27:59.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>mechanical life could</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have done the same in others.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:28:00.512 --> 00:28:03.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're suggesting someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>left a baby at our doorstep.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:28:04.182 --> 00:28:05.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Possibly.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:28:05.350 --> 00:28:06.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you think we can communicate with it?</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:28:07.185 --> 00:28:08.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, in a way, we already have.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:28:08.978 --> 00:28:11.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, it's part and parcel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of our computer now.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:28:11.356 --> 00:28:13.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But as far as direct communication</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is concerned</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:28:13.775 --> 00:28:15.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it may not be capable of that.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:28:15.360 --> 00:28:17.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We haven't seen any evidence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that this entity is sentient.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:28:17.737 --> 00:28:21.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: Maybe more like a stray puppy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's attached itself to you, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:28:21.574 --> 00:28:23.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Whatever it is, it's slowly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>disabling our station.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:28:23.701 --> 00:28:25.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>People, we've got to get it out of there.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:28:26.079 --> 00:28:29.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It came here when we downloaded</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the probe's files.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:28:29.874 --> 00:28:34.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we upload those same files back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the probe it might go with them.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:28:34.170 --> 00:28:36.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if it's fully integrated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>itself into our computer?</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:28:36.756 --> 00:28:40.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think it has.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That would make it more like a virus.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:28:40.385 --> 00:28:43.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I don't see any evidence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that it's trying to overwrite</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:28:43.513 --> 00:28:45.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>our control networks or destroy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>our systems.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:28:45.724 --> 00:28:48.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it's more likely that it simply</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>creates connections</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:28:48.852 --> 00:28:50.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>with areas of the computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that are active.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:28:50.603 --> 00:28:53.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Almost as though it feeds off the energy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the computer functions.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:28:54.023 --> 00:28:56.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I'm right, transferring</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all of its programming</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:28:56.860 --> 00:28:59.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>off the station might just solve</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>our problems.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:29:04.284 --> 00:29:07.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How long since we had any communication</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from Odo?</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:29:07.203 --> 00:29:11.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Com lines have been down over 90 minutes.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's been in there almost four hours now.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:29:12.500 --> 00:29:15.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you happen to know the schedule</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of his regenerative cycle?</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:29:15.837 --> 00:29:17.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My God, I have no idea</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:29:18.631 --> 00:29:21.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but if he doesn't get back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to his pail in time...</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:29:29.100 --> 00:29:34.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Subspace emitter aligned.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Outgoing data stream activated.</i></c.bg_transparent>

528
00:29:34.230 --> 00:29:37.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, upload</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all probe command sequences</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:29:37.859 --> 00:29:39.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>back to probe's computer.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:29:40.028 --> 00:29:41.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand by.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:29:41.613 --> 00:29:45.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Unable to complete requested function.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Please abort and retry.</i></c.bg_transparent>

532
00:29:46.993 --> 00:29:48.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reset subspace emitter.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:29:50.121 --> 00:29:51.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reinitialize data stream.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:29:52.999 --> 00:29:56.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Receptors open. Control relays activated.</i></c.bg_transparent>

535
00:29:58.213 --> 00:30:02.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Upload all probe command sequences</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back to probe's computers.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:30:02.842 --> 00:30:04.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

537
00:30:09.307 --> 00:30:12.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not as easy as I thought</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it would be, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:30:15.647 --> 00:30:19.901 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is it just the lights or the heat, too?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't bring any warm clothes.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:30:19.984 --> 00:30:22.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure it's just temporary.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:30:22.946 --> 00:30:26.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've been reading the reports</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your Chief of Operations, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:30:27.033 --> 00:30:30.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They gave me the impression</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that he was a competent engineer.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:30:30.578 --> 00:30:33.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief O'Brien?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>One of the best in Starfleet.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:30:33.498 --> 00:30:35.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then why aren't the backup</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>systems functioning?</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:30:36.292 --> 00:30:37.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you know...</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:30:37.669 --> 00:30:42.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Out here on the edge of the frontier</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's just one adventure after another.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:30:42.841 --> 00:30:45.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why don't I escort you all back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your quarters,</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:30:45.635 --> 00:30:49.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>where I'm sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we can all wait this one out.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:31:00.316 --> 00:31:01.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But enough about me.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:31:03.403 --> 00:31:04.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:31:04.821 --> 00:31:07.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enough about me. Tell me about yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:31:10.159 --> 00:31:12.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm really a private man.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:31:13.872 --> 00:31:15.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, of course you are.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:31:19.085 --> 00:31:20.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that hair real?</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:31:23.214 --> 00:31:25.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is real in that it is me.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:31:26.718 --> 00:31:28.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is not real hair.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:31:29.971 --> 00:31:30.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did you do it?</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:31:31.431 --> 00:31:32.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your hair.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:31:34.893 --> 00:31:36.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It took a great deal of practice.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:31:37.729 --> 00:31:39.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You studied hairstyles?</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:31:40.231 --> 00:31:41.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:31:42.525 --> 00:31:46.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you must know I imitated the hairstyle</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:31:46.279 --> 00:31:48.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of the Bajoran man who was assigned to me.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:31:49.824 --> 00:31:50.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Assigned?</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:31:52.327 --> 00:31:57.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To study me at the research center.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He was a scientist.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:31:58.458 --> 00:32:02.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mean that's how you grew up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in a laboratory?</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:32:03.671 --> 00:32:07.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did not grow up as you think of it.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:32:07.800 --> 00:32:11.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was merely a transition</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from what I used to be...</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:32:12.680 --> 00:32:14.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To what I learned to become.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:32:15.808 --> 00:32:16.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:32:19.354 --> 00:32:21.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It sounds very lonely to me.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:32:24.984 --> 00:32:26.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was always very self-sufficient.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:32:29.155 --> 00:32:32.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure you had to be...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>uh, to survive...</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:32:33.409 --> 00:32:36.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Being... being so different</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from everyone else.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:32:40.458 --> 00:32:41.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:32:42.210 --> 00:32:43.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:32:44.462 --> 00:32:45.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Com lines are still down.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:32:46.547 --> 00:32:48.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what's taking so long.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:32:48.758 --> 00:32:51.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure you're all right?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You look warm.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:32:51.344 --> 00:32:52.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's nothing. I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:32:56.599 --> 00:32:59.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I can't imagine how it must have been.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:33:00.395 --> 00:33:03.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, if it bothers you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to talk about this...</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:33:03.106 --> 00:33:03.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:33:06.526 --> 00:33:07.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What was it like?</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:33:07.944 --> 00:33:11.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess you could say</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I was the life of the party.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:33:12.365 --> 00:33:14.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:33:14.826 --> 00:33:16.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My way of trying to fit in.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:33:17.620 --> 00:33:20.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I found I could be entertaining.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:33:20.415 --> 00:33:24.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Odo, be a chair." I'm a chair.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>"Odo, be a razorcat." I'm a razorcat.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:33:24.419 --> 00:33:25.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Life of the party.</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:33:26.254 --> 00:33:27.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:33:28.089 --> 00:33:30.049 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hate parties.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:33:32.301 --> 00:33:35.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, perhaps you've been going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the wrong ones.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:33:37.432 --> 00:33:38.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come to one of mine, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:33:39.392 --> 00:33:42.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll make sure that all the guests</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are there to entertain you.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:33:47.150 --> 00:33:48.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:33:48.443 --> 00:33:50.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, now, you're not well.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:33:51.195 --> 00:33:52.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, it's fine. It's just, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:33:56.951 --> 00:34:00.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you I turn into a liquid</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>every 16 hours.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:34:02.957 --> 00:34:05.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm in hour 15.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:34:15.553 --> 00:34:16.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ready, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:34:16.763 --> 00:34:18.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How long do you expect it to take?</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:34:18.681 --> 00:34:19.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, if it works</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:34:19.682 --> 00:34:21.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we ought to be able</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get all the probe's files</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:34:21.434 --> 00:34:23.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>manually transferred</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the six isolinear rods</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:34:23.811 --> 00:34:25.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in less than 60 seconds.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:34:25.146 --> 00:34:26.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's do it.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:34:27.273 --> 00:34:31.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, run a level-1 diagnostic</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of all power systems on board.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:34:31.736 --> 00:34:34.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Requested function</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>will require 43 minutes.</i></c.bg_transparent>

609
00:34:34.489 --> 00:34:35.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand by.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:34:37.658 --> 00:34:40.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Computer, give me an analysis</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:34:40.328 --> 00:34:42.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>of all Cardassian traffic</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>along the border.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:34:42.997 --> 00:34:45.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Processing long-range sensors. Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

613
00:34:47.710 --> 00:34:50.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: Computer create</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a historical data base</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:34:50.630 --> 00:34:52.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for all known wormhole activity.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:34:52.799 --> 00:34:55.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( stuttering )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Indicate time parameters.</i></c.bg_transparent>

616
00:34:55.259 --> 00:34:56.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: All known occurrences.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:34:57.220 --> 00:35:01.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( slowly )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Requested function</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>will require subspace link-up.</i></c.bg_transparent>

618
00:35:02.266 --> 00:35:06.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: In that case, create a subspace</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>link with Nehru Colony,</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:35:06.395 --> 00:35:10.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>New France Colony,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and Corado I Transmitter Array.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:35:11.067 --> 00:35:16.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( stuttering )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Attempting link-up.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by...</i></c.bg_transparent>

621
00:35:17.448 --> 00:35:21.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, access musical files</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Bajor Master Data Banks</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:35:21.160 --> 00:35:23.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and create a concert program</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of Bajoran serenas.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:35:23.871 --> 00:35:27.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand... by...</i></c.bg_transparent>

624
00:35:27.500 --> 00:35:31.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( fading )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Unable to...</i></c.bg_transparent>

625
00:35:32.213 --> 00:35:33.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand...</i></c.bg_transparent>

626
00:35:36.259 --> 00:35:39.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm reading a huge plasma surge</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Habitat Ring.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:35:39.720 --> 00:35:42.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You tell Commander Sisko that I expect</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that probe briefing</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:35:42.181 --> 00:35:45.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to be held on schedule,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>lights or no lights.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:35:45.184 --> 00:35:47.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will surely pass that on, Ambassador--</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:35:51.440 --> 00:35:54.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got a plasma explosion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in corridor H-12-A, guest quarters.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:35:54.735 --> 00:35:55.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The computer's not responding.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:35:56.028 --> 00:35:58.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>None of the fire suppression</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>systems are coming on line.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:35:58.239 --> 00:35:59.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm reading four life-forms</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in that corridor.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:35:59.991 --> 00:36:02.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, you're with me. Chief,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>get an emergency crew down there.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:36:02.618 --> 00:36:04.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-We'll need manual fire gear.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:36:04.662 --> 00:36:06.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:36:21.721 --> 00:36:25.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:36:42.575 --> 00:36:43.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Phasers at maximum.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:36:49.832 --> 00:36:52.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Toranium inlay, Cardassian design</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I should have guessed.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:36:52.418 --> 00:36:54.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're going to need a bipolar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>torch to get through it.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:36:54.795 --> 00:36:56.047 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then get a message to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:36:56.172 --> 00:36:58.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell them it's going to take us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a while to get inside.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:36:58.257 --> 00:37:00.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If they can't get the fire</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>suppression systems on line</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:37:00.426 --> 00:37:01.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we're going to lose our people in there.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:37:01.802 --> 00:37:02.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:37:04.847 --> 00:37:07.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not paying any attention to me.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:37:08.267 --> 00:37:12.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess it just doesn't want to leave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>like a scared puppy.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:37:13.147 --> 00:37:17.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have no idea how long that probe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was tumbling through space, maybe years,</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:37:17.526 --> 00:37:19.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with that life-form alone on board.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:37:19.946 --> 00:37:22.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's sort of like shutting up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a puppy in a room, you know?</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:37:23.616 --> 00:37:26.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had a pup once. If I had to lock him up</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:37:26.452 --> 00:37:28.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>he'd scratch forever</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the door trying to get out.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:37:29.205 --> 00:37:31.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not sure I know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you're getting at.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:37:31.582 --> 00:37:34.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pups don't like to be left alone.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They like attention.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:37:35.503 --> 00:37:37.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This one is certainly getting a lot of it.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:37:38.005 --> 00:37:38.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:37:39.757 --> 00:37:41.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So it's no wonder</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it doesn't want to leave.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:37:42.343 --> 00:37:44.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>OK, but how is that going to help us?</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:37:44.845 --> 00:37:46.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everything we've seen suggests</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:37:46.347 --> 00:37:48.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that this entity likes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be where the action is.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:37:49.433 --> 00:37:52.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems to feed off the energy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of an active computer.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:37:52.478 --> 00:37:55.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've been trying to separate it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from what it thrives on.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:37:56.274 --> 00:37:58.067 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got to do the exact opposite.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:37:58.651 --> 00:37:59.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The exact opposite?</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:38:00.236 --> 00:38:03.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant, I've got to build a doghouse.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:38:05.074 --> 00:38:08.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( labored breathing )</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:38:14.959 --> 00:38:16.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:38:17.586 --> 00:38:18.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:38:22.133 --> 00:38:22.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo out.</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:38:23.634 --> 00:38:25.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo, turn around.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:38:26.178 --> 00:38:29.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't. It's beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:38:30.224 --> 00:38:31.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:38:32.727 --> 00:38:33.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't understand.</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:38:35.313 --> 00:38:37.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one has ever seen me like this before.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:38:39.275 --> 00:38:41.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not even the scientist</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who was assigned to you?</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:38:42.194 --> 00:38:43.029 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That was different.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:38:44.030 --> 00:38:45.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was only research to him.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:38:47.533 --> 00:38:49.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you don't have to be ashamed with me.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:38:50.494 --> 00:38:52.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not ashamed.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:38:53.456 --> 00:38:55.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a private matter, that's all.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:38:58.461 --> 00:39:00.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How can I make it easier for you?</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:39:01.964 --> 00:39:03.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't.</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:39:03.716 --> 00:39:04.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:39:13.517 --> 00:39:14.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:39:15.394 --> 00:39:16.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My hair.</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:39:25.654 --> 00:39:28.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one's ever seen me like this.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:39:30.284 --> 00:39:31.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:39:32.912 --> 00:39:34.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It looks fine.</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:39:36.415 --> 00:39:37.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It looks ordinary.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:39:38.709 --> 00:39:40.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never cared to be ordinary.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:39:42.838 --> 00:39:45.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you see, Odo,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even we non-shape-shifters</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:39:45.925 --> 00:39:47.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>have to change who we are once in a while.</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:39:51.055 --> 00:39:54.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are not at all what I expected.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:39:57.937 --> 00:40:00.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one's ever paid me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a greater compliment.</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:40:08.697 --> 00:40:13.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... cannot hold my shape any longer.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:40:16.997 --> 00:40:18.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let go.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:40:20.793 --> 00:40:22.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll take care of you.</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:40:22.503 --> 00:40:24.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:40:31.637 --> 00:40:35.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: We're going to need portable</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>oxygen and get anything</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:40:35.349 --> 00:40:38.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bashir has in stock to treat plasma burns.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Have a runabout ready</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:40:38.561 --> 00:40:40.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to evacuate these people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to Bajor if we need to.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:40:40.354 --> 00:40:41.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:40:44.442 --> 00:40:45.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anara?</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:40:46.026 --> 00:40:47.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The subprogram is ready, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:40:48.737 --> 00:40:52.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, analyze subprogram</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>labeled "Pup."</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:40:53.242 --> 00:40:57.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Requested subprogram is a series</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>of bi-directional data transfer</i></c.bg_transparent>

707
00:40:57.163 --> 00:40:58.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>and monitoring commands.</i></c.bg_transparent>

708
00:40:58.914 --> 00:41:03.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reroute all main computer backup functions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>through this subprogram.</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:41:03.961 --> 00:41:06.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>All backup functions rerouted.</i></c.bg_transparent>

710
00:41:06.714 --> 00:41:07.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Great.</c.bg_transparent>

711
00:41:08.757 --> 00:41:10.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>OK, computer. Now, listen carefully.</c.bg_transparent>

712
00:41:11.385 --> 00:41:14.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to transfer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all probe command sequences</c.bg_transparent>

713
00:41:14.597 --> 00:41:17.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>out of core memory</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and into the subprogram Pup.</c.bg_transparent>

714
00:41:17.975 --> 00:41:19.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

715
00:41:21.437 --> 00:41:23.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Transfer complete.</i></c.bg_transparent>

716
00:41:25.065 --> 00:41:28.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dax to Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Fire suppression is responding.</i></c.bg_transparent>

717
00:41:28.194 --> 00:41:30.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>All systems are back on line.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Can you get in?</i></c.bg_transparent>

718
00:41:34.617 --> 00:41:36.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're in, Dax. Stand by.</c.bg_transparent>

719
00:41:38.662 --> 00:41:41.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( electrical hissing and popping )</c.bg_transparent>

720
00:41:57.932 --> 00:42:00.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'd better advise Starfleet Command.</c.bg_transparent>

721
00:42:01.143 --> 00:42:02.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rattling )</c.bg_transparent>

722
00:42:06.190 --> 00:42:07.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you all right?</c.bg_transparent>

723
00:42:08.275 --> 00:42:09.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: Here, take my hand,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

724
00:42:11.237 --> 00:42:12.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Watch your head.</c.bg_transparent>

725
00:42:14.448 --> 00:42:15.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

726
00:42:16.033 --> 00:42:17.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Call me Taxco.</c.bg_transparent>

727
00:42:19.161 --> 00:42:20.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ambassador, are you all right?</c.bg_transparent>

728
00:42:20.621 --> 00:42:22.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes. Thanks to Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

729
00:42:26.877 --> 00:42:30.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Doctor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was remarkably calm and logical,</c.bg_transparent>

730
00:42:30.172 --> 00:42:33.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for a man of his years,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>under such severe conditions.</c.bg_transparent>

731
00:42:33.884 --> 00:42:36.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be putting him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in for a commendation.</c.bg_transparent>

732
00:42:40.766 --> 00:42:42.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nice work, Dr. Bashir.</c.bg_transparent>

733
00:42:43.394 --> 00:42:45.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just in the right place</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the right time, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

734
00:42:53.320 --> 00:42:55.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, it's about time.</c.bg_transparent>

735
00:42:58.117 --> 00:43:03.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... know that wasn't exactly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you had in mind</c.bg_transparent>

736
00:43:03.497 --> 00:43:04.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for your picnic.</c.bg_transparent>

737
00:43:06.584 --> 00:43:09.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When it comes to picnics</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the only thing that really matters</c.bg_transparent>

738
00:43:10.004 --> 00:43:11.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is the company.</c.bg_transparent>

739
00:43:12.506 --> 00:43:16.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your sensitivity and discretion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are appreciated.</c.bg_transparent>

740
